--- !u!114 &344360155
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 344360153}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ce18765a41c63c34597aa14dc4ea1f8c, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  dialogueBox: {fileID: 1374500641}
  dialogueActive: 1
  sentences:
  - Oh no! You're stuck on an abandoned island...
  - You need to figure out how to survive. Your only friends right now are the trees,
    the wind and a parrot.
  - Look to the top right. This is your health, hunger and warmth panel. To survive
    you need to eat food and keep warm at night.
  - 'The only way to keep warm is to make a bonfire... Here''s a little clue: there
    are lots of trees around you which you can cut!'
  - 'Remember to always use the necessary tools... somewhere on this map there''s
    a chest where you can find them. '
  - To buy seeds which you can later plant visit your parrot friend. Different seeds
    have different prices due to their growing time and health and hunger increase.
  - On the top left you can see what time it is and also how many points you currently
    have. You can use them to buy seeds! Perform actions in the game to gather them.
  - You can see your inventory after clicking E. Also remember you can always pause
    the game after clicking P!
  - But don't worry... if you last long enough help will come to your rescue. Just
    don't starve yourself or freeze to death.
  - Find the necessary tools to help you survive. You're already feeling hungry and
    it's starting to get dark soon... Good luck!
  textDisplay: {fileID: 1828790188}
  typingSpeed: 0.015
  pressToContinue: {fileID: 1566021790}
